# Bulk empirical sweep TSVs from the libwebp parity audit (PR #37).
# Regeneratable via `dev/empirical_sweep.rs` against a CID22 / CLIC /
# ImageMagick corpus. Kept on block storage at /mnt/v/output/zenwebp/audit/
# rather than in git — they add ~720 KB of compressed pack churn for data
# that's a single command away. The summary in
# `differences/05-empirical-analysis.md` is what callers actually consume;
# the per-batch baselines under `differences/baselines/` are the audit
# progression.
differences/05-empirical-*.tsv
